OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry today with strong
OL,6,Fsunshine, turning hazy at times.
OL,7,FFeeling hot and increasingly humid
OL,8,Fwith light winds. A small chance of a
OL,9,Ffew showers late in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy at first with a few
OL,12,Fevening showers and a chance of a few
OL,13,Fthunderstorms. Rain then clearing to
OL,14,Fleave a dry, warm and humid night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FVery hot and humid on Tuesday
OL,17,Fwith strong sunshine and light winds.
OL,18,FHigh humidity will intensify the heat
OL,19,Fmaking it feel rather uncomfortable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
