OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FExtreme heat on Wednesday and Thursday
OL,7,Fwith high humidity and very warm and
OL,8,Fmuggy nights. Strong sunshine at
OL,9,Ftimes, but turning increasingly cloudy
OL,10,Ffrom Thursday. Slightly less hot
OL,11,FFriday.
